Text: I was in daman and diu a part of union territory of India. It started with a
  pleasant trip with friends.... But being into a room was killing with just one friend
  i left down to explore the place at night 2 we were drunk a bottle down. All sitting
  inside the room expecting us to be back in half an hour, well we were just sitting
  near the beach side with a pack of ciggerates and enjoying the night breeze from
  the sea it was so good that I was making me feel meditative. We sat their for time
  but that wasn't enough taking a leap forward we ended up sitting nearly close to
  the barrigate of the beach with a phone and couple of cards (bank debit). After
  waking up in the morning figured out myself sleeping the whole night near that beach
  and ending up loosing my phone,fingers crossed the cards were still there but it
  was such a deep sleep that loosing phone was least bothered than ending up sleeping
  into the cozy breeze. That was just fun for me after that I didn't stop exploring
